data.description: This brilliantly designed custom home awaits you on Northshore Drive in the preferred community of Walden on Lake Conroe and is majestically elevated from street level atop three lots covering approximately one half acre of land with180 linear feet of street frontage offering breathtaking water views of the lake from multiple vantage points. This 2-story home with its sleek architectural design offers an estate-style living with its property surrounded on three sides by undeveloped forested lots and defined by professionally landscaped grounds, 100+ yr old trees and a meandering driveway leading to a controlled gate access into a private iron fenced back yard. A stately entrance is defined by way of a large elevated porch and arched transom windowed doorway and highlighted by a stunning foyer boasting 20 foot ceilings, a grand circular staircase and spacious gallery for welcoming guests. From there you are captivated by the magnitude of this 2-story great room and its plantation shuttered windows, an elegant wood burning fireplace and the overall rich boldness embodied throughout the home by the finer accents of custom craftsmanship. Let your imagination run wild at the endless possibilities for entertaining family and friends in this creatively designed home where the great room flows seamlessly, depending on the occasion, to either the formal patio  through french doors, or into a luxurious dining area connecting to two separate wet bar and cooking islands and an expansive kitchen area with breakfast nook. An additional patio is right outside the breakfast area and both patios invite you to enjoy your favorite latte, cocktail or beverage of choice and take in the beauty of your surroundings. The perfect beginning or end to any day may be found in the grand master suite where intentional and generous proportions of this bedroom afford additional space to create the perfect sanctuary for full retreat and relaxation. Whether you desire to optimize usage of this space with a study/workspace, or a spacious sitting area or both, this room can accommodate your needs. A grand master bathroom includes a jetted tub, large shower, two separate vanities, private toilet, and large walk-in closet topping off this impressive grand master suite. On the second floor, two bedrooms, a 3/4 bathroom and a walk-in attic space complete this jewel of a home. The home has 3 separate HVAC zones for the upstairs, downstairs, and grand master suite and features a large utility room with sink and can accommodate an additional refrigerator and/or freezer. An oversized garage features areas for a workspace or workbench, tool and equipment storage if desired and a private toilet for your convenience. Additionally, a new roof was installed in 2020 and newly carpeted in 2021.
data.whatILove: This majestic home is one of a kind and uniquely designed to optimize views and enjoy an elegant lifestyle. Not only located in the exclusive amenity-rich Walden community, this home is located within the highly acclaimed Montgomery Independent School District.
